Description: Fits semiparametric linear and multilevel models with non-parametric additive Bayesian additive regression tree (BART; Chipman, George, and McCulloch (2010) <doi:10.1214/09-AOAS285>) components and gradient-sampled parametric ones. The parametric conditional is drawn with a hand-derived analytic log-posterior gradient and the WALNUTS sampler (vendored from <https://github.com/flatironinstitute/walnuts>, commit 5854be8; MIT licensed, (c) 2025 Bob Carpenter). Multilevel models can be expressed using 'lme4' syntax (Bates, Maechler, Bolker, and Walker (2015) <doi:10.18637/jss.v067.i01>).
